title: Strengthen Your Inner Man | Victoria Osteen

description:
God wants to fill us with new strength. When you make it a habit to strengthen your inner man, your life will be transformed for the better! 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
